'''钛酸锂电池'''（{{lang-en|Lithium-titanate battery}}，缩写LTO）是一种[[蓄電池|可充电电池]]，优势是充电快于其他种类的[[锂离子电池|锂离子电池]]<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Fast charging of lithium-ion batteries at all temperatures|url=https://www.pnas.org/content/115/28/7266|last=Yang|first=Xiao-Guang|last2=Zhang|first2=Guangsheng|date=2018-07-10|journal=Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences|issue=28|doi=10.1073/pnas.1807115115|volume=115|pages=7266–7271|language=en|issn=0027-8424|pmid=29941558|last3=Ge|first3=Shanhai|last4=Wang|first4=Chao-Yang}}</ref> ，但它的能量密度低很多。

== 当前用途 ==
[[三菱汽车|三菱]][[三菱iMiEV电动汽车|i-MiEV]]<ref name="IntegrityExports">{{Cite news|url=http://integrityexports.com/2011/06/18/mitsubishi-chooses-toshiba-scib-battery-for-evs/|title=Mitsubishi Chooses Super-Efficient Toshiba SCiB Battery For EVs|publisher=Integrity Exports|date=2011-06-18|accessdate=2011-06-18}}</ref>[[电动载具|电动车]]的部分日本版使用钛酸电池，[[本田技研工业|本田]]也将其用于EV-neo电动自行车和[[本田飞度|Fit EV]]。 <ref name="GCC">{{Cite web|title=Toshiba's SCiB battery for the Fit EV|url=http://www.greencarcongress.com/2011/11/scib-20111117.html|date=Nov 17, 2011|publisher=Green Car Congress}}</ref> <ref name="GCC2">{{Cite web|title=Honda begins European demonstration program of EV-neo electric scooter|url=http://www.greencarcongress.com/2011/06/evneo20110615.html|date=Jun 15, 2011|publisher=Green Car Congress}}</ref>Tosa概念电动公共汽车也有使用。<ref>[http://www.tosa2013.com/en TOSA2013] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140525200937/http://www.tosa2013.com/en|date=2014-05-25}}: The project aims to introduce a new system of mass transport with electric "flash" recharging of the buses at selected stops.</ref>由于其较高的安全性和充电能力，钛酸锂电池同时被一些汽车音频应用以及移动医疗设备采用。 <ref>{{Cite web|title=All About Batteries, Part 12: Lithium Titanate (LTO)|url=https://www.eetimes.com/author.asp?section_id=36&doc_id=1325358}}</ref>

[[三星集团|三星]][[三星Galaxy_Note_20|Galaxy Note 20 Ultra 5G]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Specs {{!}} Samsung Galaxy Note20 & Note20 Ultra|url=https://www.samsung.com/global/galaxy/galaxy-note20/specs/|accessdate=2020-08-06|work=The Official Samsung Galaxy Site|language=en}}</ref>随附的S笔中使用了钛酸锂电池。

根据Weatherflow Co.的文章<ref>{{Cite web|title=Solar Power for Tempest|url=https://help.weatherflow.com/hc/en-us/articles/360048877194-Solar-Power-for-Tempest|accessdate=2020-08-23|work=help.weatherflow.com|language=en}}</ref> ，Tempest个人气象站设备包含一个1300mAh钛酸锂电池，该电池通过四个[[太阳能电池板|太阳能电池板]]充电，“每两周需要至少4个小时的充足光照”。

== 化学 ==
钛酸锂电池是一种改进的锂离子电池，在其[[陽極|陽極]]表面使用[[钛酸锂|钛酸锂]][[纳米晶体|纳米晶体]]代替[[碳|碳]]。这样阳极的表面积约为100平方米/克，而碳的表面积为3平方米/克，该差异使[[电子|电子]]能快速进入和离开阳极，因此快速充电成为可能，并可在需要时提供大电流。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Charge a battery in just six minutes|url=https://www.newscientist.com/article.ns?id=dn7081|accessdate=2010-07-06|author=Graham-Rowe, Duncan|date=7 March 2005|publisher=New Scientist}}</ref>钛酸锂电池可持续3000到7000个充电循环<ref>{{Cite web|title=LTO Batteries|url=http://www.batteryspace.com/Lithium-Titanate-Battery.aspx}}</ref> ；一份资料称在{{Convert|55|°C|°F|0|abbr=on}}而非标准的{{Convert|25|°C|°F|0|abbr=on}}环境下充放电，容量降至80%前约有1000次循环寿命。<ref>https://www.researchgate.net/publication/272646684_Cycle_Life_of_Commercial_Lithium-Ion_Batteries_with_Lithium_Titanium_Oxide_Anodes_in_Electric_Vehicles</ref>

钛酸锂电池的缺点是其固有电压较低（2.4 V），因此有较低的[[比能|比能]]（约30–110 Wh / kg{{R|EETimes}}），逊于常规[[锂离子电池|锂离子电池]]技术的固有电压3.7 V<ref>{{Cite web|title=Green Car Congress: Toshiba Developing 3.0 Ah High Power SCiB Li-Ion Cell for HEV Applications|url=http://www.greencarcongress.com/2008/05/toshiba-develop.html|accessdate=2010-07-07|author=|date=21 May 2008}}</ref>，尽管有报道称某些钛酸锂电池的[[能量密度|能量密度]]高达177 Wh/L<ref name="EETimes" />。

